  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAccessor, IContainerItemAccessor<Integer>, IPropertyAccessor, Cloneable

    public final class LeafArrayItemAccessorImpl
extends AbstractArrayItemAccessorImpl
    The final class LeafArrayItemAccessorImpl models a concrete implementation of the IAccessor interface, responsible for accessing simple type items of ArrayS, such as Integer or EnumS.
    Since:
    1.0.0
